          "note": "No. 4: the darkest and most uncomfortable Tarantino movie for him, built around DiCaprio's Calvin Candie, though he thinks the ending is overkill."
        },
        {
          "title": "True Romance",
          "year": 1993,
          "note": "No. 5: written by Tarantino, directed by Tony Scott; his entry point before he'd even seen Reservoir Dogs."
        }
